sequenceDiagram
    participant Pipeline as Platform Pipeline
    participant Service as Service (e.g., Enriching)
    participant TechA as Tech A (e.g., Vendor API)
    participant TechB as Tech B (e.g., Local Model)

    Pipeline->>Service: execute_batch([item1, item2])
    activate Service
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over Service, TechB: Concurrent execution for each item
        Service->>TechA: execute(item1)
        Service->>TechB: execute(item1)
        TechA-->>Service: Output or None (Error)
        TechB-->>Service: Output or None (Error)
    end
    
    Service-->>Pipeline: list[ServiceResult]
    deactivate Service
